high_descs: Turn around and go near the cabinet.
Take the fork from the cabinet.
Turn around and go near the side table.
Put the fork on the side table.
Turn around and go near the bed.
Take another fork from the bed.
Turn around and go near the side table.
Put the fork on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Collect the fork and placed it on the side table.

high_descs: Turn right, continue to the bottom, turn left. Enter the room, turn left. Go to the cabinet and turn left.
Open the right door and take out the fork, close the door.
Turn around, move closer to the bed. Turn to the right. Approach the sidetable.
Place the fork on the sidetable parallel to the wall.
Turn around, when you reach the wall, turn left. Reach the middle of the bed and turn left.
Take the fork.
Turn left, at the end of the bed, turn right. Reach the sidetable.
Place the fork on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Find two forks and place them on the sidetable.

high_descs: Turn left to head down the passage and head left to reach the bedroom cabinet on the left.
Pick up the fork from the cabinet.
Turn around and head to the side table on the right.
Put the fork on the side table.
Turn around to head to the bottom of the bed.
Pick up the fork from the bed.
Head to the side table on the left.
Put the fork on the side table.
anns.task_desc: Put two forks on the side table.
